<h1>Your Login Link</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>You requested a login link for <%= @organization %>. Click the link below to sign in:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Sign In", @login_url %></p>

<p>This link can only be used once and will expire shortly. If you did not request this link, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The <%= @organization %> Team</p>
